                    <h3 class="mb-0">Common Errors Observed in Processing Maturity Benefit Claims</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>(a)</strong> Non processing of Appx 'G' in case of Offrs and JCOs & OR proceeding on pre mature retirement.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>(b)</strong> Incorrect/incomplete details in Appx G.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>(c)</strong> Details of service in the rank of OR and/or JCO in respect of officers granted commission post OR/JCO service is also required to be filled to obtain additional maturity amount for contribution made to AGIF scheme as JCOs & OR.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>(d)</strong> Non clearance of loans taken from AGIF.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>(e)</strong> Non submission of two passport size photographs of NOK.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>(f)</strong> Non submission of copy of SOS Part II Order in case of pre mature retirement.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>(g)</strong> Address given in the Appx G is not the one where the offr is residing
                            as he may have taken re-emp / house not yet ready, etc. Documents of such addresses
                            are invariably recd back in the Dte, undelivered by the postel authorities.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>(h)</strong> Offr on secondment to est not under MoD need to monitor their monthly
                            subscriptions to AGIF personally.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>(j)</strong> Details reqd for electronic payment like IFSC Code & cancelled cheques not
                            being submitted.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
